t\u00f3c trong su\u1ed1t m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i sau \u0111\u00f3.<\/p>\n<p>\u2234\u00a0Tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i t\u1ea1o ki\u1ec3u, u\u1ed1n, nhu\u1ed9m m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng s\u1ee3 t\u00f3c b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng<\/p>\n<p>\u2234\u00a0Kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean b\u1ecb r\u1ee5ng t\u00f3c<\/p>\n<p><strong>KH\u00c1C BI\u1ec6T TRONG D\u1ecaCH V\u1ee4 PH\u1ee4C H\u1ed2I T\u00d3C C\u1ee6A HO\u00c0NG H\u1ed2NG<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>*\u00a0\u0110\u1ed9i ng\u0169 chuy\u00ean vi\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c truy\u1ec1n c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng t\u1eeb chuy\u00ean gia, NTM Ho\u00e0ng H\u1ed3ng, tay ngh\u1ec1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u00e8n luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 m\u00e0i d\u0169a trong nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m<\/p>\n<p>*\u00a0Gi\u00e1 c\u1ea3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n t\u01b0\u01a1ng x\u1ee9ng v\u1edbi ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p b\u1ea1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadn khi \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i t\u00f3c c\u1ee7a Ho\u00e0ng H\u1ed3ng. Ho\u00e0ng H\u1ed3ng t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Ninh B\u00ecnh, kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 thua k\u00e9m d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 l\u1edbn.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-560     lazyloaded\" title=\"[Tags]\" src=\"http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/Ph%E1%BB%A5c-h%E1%BB%93i-t%C3%B3c_04.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1021px) 100vw, 1021px\" srcset=\"http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/Ph\u1ee5c-h\u1ed3i-t\u00f3c_04.jpg 1021w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/Ph\u1ee5c-h\u1ed3i-t\u00f3c_04-300x145.jpg 300w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/Ph\u1ee5c-h\u1ed3i-t\u00f3c_04-768x372.jpg 768w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/Ph\u1ee5c-h\u1ed3i-t\u00f3c_04-260x126.jpg 260w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/Ph\u1ee5c-h\u1ed3i-t\u00f3c_04-50x24.jpg 50w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/Ph\u1ee5c-h\u1ed3i-t\u00f3c_04-576x279.jpg 576w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/Ph\u1ee5c-h\u1ed3i-t\u00f3c_04-150x73.jpg 150w\" alt=\"Ph\u1ee5c-h\u1ed3i-t\u00f3c_01 Ph\u1ee5c H\u1ed3i T\u00f3c\" width=\"1021\" height=\"495\" data-lazy-src=\"http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/Ph\u1ee5c-h\u1ed3i-t\u00f3c_04.jpg\" data-lazy-srcset=\"http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/Ph\u1ee5c-h\u1ed3i-t\u00f3c_04.jpg 1021w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/Ph\u1ee5c-h\u1ed3i-t\u00f3c_04-300x145.jpg 300w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/Ph\u1ee5c-h\u1ed3i-t\u00f3c_04-768x372.jpg 768w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/Ph\u1ee5c-h\u1ed3i-t\u00f3c_04-260x126.jpg 260w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/Ph\u1ee5c-h\u1ed3i-t\u00f3c_04-50x24.jpg 50w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/Ph\u1ee5c-h\u1ed3i-t\u00f3c_04-576x279.jpg 576w, http:\/\/thammyvienhoanghong.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/09\/Ph\u1ee5c-h\u1ed3i-t\u00f3c_04-150x73.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-sizes=\"(max-width: 1021px) 100vw, 1021px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><em>C\u01a1 s\u1edf hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Ho\u00e0ng H\u1ed3ng Salon &amp; Spa<\/em><\/p>\n<p>*\u00a0C\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i d\u1ea7u d\u01b0\u1ee1ng v\u00e0 li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t, an to\u00e0n tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi l\u00e0n da c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. Quy tr\u00ecnh nhanh ch\u00f3ng v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n.<\/p>\n<p><strong>L\u01afU \u00dd KH\u00d4NG TH\u1ec2 B\u1ece QUA TRONG PH\u1ee4C H\u1ed2I T\u00d3C<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>\u221a.N\u00ean th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean d\u01b0\u1ee1ng t\u00f3c sau khi g\u1ed9i v\u00e0 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng lo\u1ea1i d\u1ea7u g\u1ed9i, d\u1ea7u x\u1ea3 c\u00f3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i t\u00f3c h\u01b0 t\u1ed5n<\/p>\n<p>\u221a.Th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean quan s\u00e1t t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe c\u1ee7a m\u00e1i t\u00f3c, tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00f3c h\u01b0 t\u1ed5n qu\u00e1 n\u1eb7ng. M\u1ed9t khi m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng qu\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1eaft t\u1ec9a to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 ph\u1ea7n t\u00f3c \u0111\u00f3 \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c v\u00e0 nu\u00f4i d\u01b0\u1ee1ng l\u1ea1i t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u<\/p>\n<p>\u221a.Cung c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft cho t\u00f3c, tr\u00e1nh \u00e1nh n\u1eafng m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi chi\u1ebfu tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp l\u00ean t\u00f3c trong th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i.<\/p>\n<p>\u221a.T\u00f9y v\u00e0o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n th\u1eddi gian c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u00e0 kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1eefa nh\u1eefng l\u1ea7n ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i t\u00f3c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00e1c nhau. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng, trung b\u00ecnh 1 th\u00e1ng, b\u1ea1n n\u00ean \u0111i ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i t\u00f3c m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n, gh\u00e9 qua Salon \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n ch\u0103m s\u00f3c t\u00f3c to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n.<\/p>\n<p>C\u00e1i r\u0103ng c\u00e1i t\u00f3c l\u00e0 g\u00f3c con ng\u01b0\u1eddi. H\u00e3y \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eefng chuy\u00ean gia c\u1ee7a Ho\u00e0ng H\u1ed3ng Salon &amp; Spa \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn cho b\u1ea1n m\u1ed9t d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i t\u00f3c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n thi\u1ebft th\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c v\u00e0 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 m\u00e1i t\u00f3c \u0111\u1eb9p, ghi \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 cu\u1ed9c g\u1eb7p m\u1eb7t n\u00e0o.<\/p>\n<p><strong>HO\u00c0NG H\u1ed2NG SALON &amp; SPA<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>S\u1ed1 7, Ng\u00f5 62, \u0110inh Ti\u00ean Ho\u00e0ng, TP Ninh B\u00ecnh<\/p>\n<p>Tel: 0303893196<\/p>\n<p>Mobile: 0916.622.622<\/p>\n<p>T\u01b0 v\u1ea5n &amp; CSKH (24\/7): 0303 893.196<\/p>\n<p>Th\u1eddi gian l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c 8:00 \u2013 21:00 L\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea3 ng\u00e0y l\u1ec5 v\u00e0 Ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch ch\u0103m s\u00f3c, s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng h\u00f3a ch\u1ea5t t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u l\u00ean m\u00e1i t\u00f3c trong m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn m\u00e1i t\u00f3c c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u ch\u1ebb ng\u1ecdn, th\u00f4 x\u01a1, g\u00e3y r\u1ee5ng. V\u1edbi d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i t\u00f3c s\u1ed1 1 Ninh B\u00ecnh, Ho\u00e0ng H\u1ed3ng Salon [&hellip;]\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"page-right-sidebar.php","meta":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/spa3.ninhbinhweb.net\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/796"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/spa3.ninhbinhweb.net\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/spa3.ninhbinhweb.net\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/spa3.ninhbinhweb.net\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/spa3.ninhbinhweb.net\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=796"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"http:\/\/spa3.ninhbinhweb.net\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/796\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/spa3.ninhbinhweb.net\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=796"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}